data.description: Are you searching for an affordable home in a well-established neighborhood with no HOA? This 3 bed, 2 bath one level home sits on a quiet cul-de-sac and is located in the heart of West Columbia. As you enter the front door natural light greets you in the living room with an open floor plan and high ceilings. Next to the living room is the bright kitchen with loads of counter space and large dining area.   Head down the hallway to find the 3 spacious bedrooms, all with private closets. The master bedroom has an ensuite bath that is perfect for your privacy. Moving back to the kitchen area leads you out the backdoor to your very own backyard oasis that features a patio area that backs up to woods. Zoned for the award-winning Lexington 1 School District and close to shopping.  Make this home your next move, book your showing today.
